Here are common shortcut used in netBeans

Basic shortcut		
Ctrl + c		: Copy
Ctrl + v		: Paste
Ctrl + z		: Undo
Ctrl + y		: Re-do
Ctrl + E		: Delete Line


Other Shortcut
Alt + scroll_up		      : Zoom in
Alt + scroll_down	      : Zoom out
Ctrl + Space 		        : Autocomplete
Ctrl + R		            : Rename the selected class, method, or variable
Alt + scroll_up	      	: Zoom in
Alt + scroll_down      	: Zoom out
Ctrl + Shfit + up/down	: Duplicate up/down
Ctrl + F		            : Find
Ctrl + H		            : Replace

psvm + tab		: create public static void main
sout + tab		: create System.out.println
if + tab		  : if shortcut
fori          : for shortcut
dowhile       : do while shortcut

